description:
globs: **/*.sh
alwaysApply: false
---
- All shell scripts should have help text that tells how to invoke them, what each argument is, and an example of each argument.
- Shell scripts with `#!/bin/sh` should be compatible with busybox, and use the busybox command set if possible.
- Shell scripts with `#!/usr/bin/env bash` or `#!/usr/bin/bash` should be compatible with bash >=5.0
- All shell scripts should pass shellcheck
